WEBVTT

00:00:14.279 --> 00:00:15.839
Attack together! Kill him!

00:00:33.280 --> 00:00:34.880
You... you're back.

00:00:35.600 --> 00:00:37.759
If you dare drop your sword again, I'll kill you first.

00:00:56.719 --> 00:00:57.679
Impossible...

00:00:58.539 --> 00:01:00.880
My cultivation now shakes the heavens and earth.

00:01:01.320 --> 00:01:03.200
Why do I feel like a child before him?

00:01:05.519 --> 00:01:06.900
Now, only the two of us remain.

00:01:07.239 --> 00:01:09.140
We must work together for even a slim chance to survive.

00:01:12.400 --> 00:01:13.280
You bitch!

00:01:17.180 --> 00:01:17.819
Chen Yuanqi.

00:01:18.319 --> 00:01:19.000
Spare me!

00:01:19.379 --> 00:01:20.760
I can call you my sworn father.

00:01:21.500 --> 00:01:22.700
You beast!

00:01:23.480 --> 00:01:25.180
Give me back Xiao Qiu's life!

00:01:44.060 --> 00:01:46.400
Husband, something's wrong!

00:01:46.519 --> 00:01:48.840
Chen Yuanqi is attacking with Lie Shumei and Jiang Yumeng!

00:01:49.099 --> 00:01:49.780
It doesn't matter.

00:01:50.480 --> 00:01:51.959
I've regained my strength.

00:01:52.420 --> 00:01:54.939
Insignificant clown, not worth fearing.

00:02:05.780 --> 00:02:07.500
Fools who don't know their place.

00:02:07.799 --> 00:02:09.479
They've come to die on their own.

00:02:13.680 --> 00:02:14.759
Dugu Zhantian.

00:02:15.680 --> 00:02:16.340
Today,

00:02:17.080 --> 00:02:19.580
I will use the blood of your entire demon clan

00:02:20.379 --> 00:02:21.740
to honor Xiao Qiu.

00:02:22.159 --> 00:02:22.900
My mother,

00:02:23.680 --> 00:02:25.900
and all the innocent souls who died.

00:02:26.180 --> 00:02:27.520
Return my father's life!

00:02:30.979 --> 00:02:32.379
Just you lot?

00:02:37.159 --> 00:02:38.379
Ignorant fools.

00:02:38.840 --> 00:02:41.560
Enough talk! Your life is mine!

00:02:55.419 --> 00:02:56.819
Yuanqi, are you alright?

00:03:18.620 --> 00:03:21.699
Let me see my own fate.

00:04:07.780 --> 00:04:09.439
Dugu Zhantian

00:04:10.659 --> 00:04:12.159
Supreme ruler of the Three Realms

00:04:14.520 --> 00:04:15.759
Countless oppressed

00:04:16.680 --> 00:04:17.980
Lives as worthless as grass

00:04:19.779 --> 00:04:21.079
Heaven’s Decree is set

00:04:21.720 --> 00:04:22.920
It cannot be changed

00:04:24.980 --> 00:04:25.720
Why

00:04:27.519 --> 00:04:28.379
Why

00:04:29.319 --> 00:04:31.000
Why is it like this

00:04:36.459 --> 00:04:37.660
Is Heaven’s Decree

00:04:39.319 --> 00:04:40.740
truly unchangeable

00:04:43.160 --> 00:04:44.019
Chen Yuanqi

00:04:44.779 --> 00:04:46.060
Do you see it

00:04:46.680 --> 00:04:48.199
The Heaven’s Tome within you

00:04:49.560 --> 00:04:51.639
clearly records

00:04:52.379 --> 00:04:56.160
I alone am the true supreme of this world

00:04:56.759 --> 00:04:58.279
Heaven’s Decree favors me

00:05:00.759 --> 00:05:02.079
All living beings

00:05:03.860 --> 00:05:06.060
are but a few strokes in the Heaven’s Tome

00:05:07.019 --> 00:05:08.759
But if these few strokes

00:05:09.439 --> 00:05:11.420
decide the suffering of all

00:05:12.279 --> 00:05:14.939
then the oppressed will never rise

00:05:17.019 --> 00:05:18.459
What’s the point of such a Heaven’s Tome

00:05:19.220 --> 00:05:20.800
Why should it exist at all

00:05:21.740 --> 00:05:22.939
What are you doing

00:05:25.579 --> 00:05:27.279
I was revived by the Heaven’s Tome

00:05:27.879 --> 00:05:28.980
If the Heaven’s Tome is destroyed

00:05:29.660 --> 00:05:31.120
I won’t live much longer either

00:05:33.879 --> 00:05:35.439
But even if I die

00:05:35.920 --> 00:05:40.360
I’ll fight for a sliver of hope for the oppressed

00:05:41.920 --> 00:05:44.160
Break!

00:05:54.300 --> 00:05:55.259
Dugu Zhantian

00:05:56.519 --> 00:05:58.519
Now that the Heaven’s Tome is destroyed

00:05:59.079 --> 00:06:00.259
everyone’s fate

00:06:01.060 --> 00:06:02.860
is no longer bound by the Heaven’s Tome

00:06:03.519 --> 00:06:05.600
Even if I die today

00:06:05.920 --> 00:06:10.240
someone will avenge me and kill you one day

00:06:12.959 --> 00:06:16.959
Even if the Heaven’s Tome is destroyed, fate cannot be changed

00:06:39.420 --> 00:06:40.139
Divine Lady

00:06:41.579 --> 00:06:42.240
Yuanqi

00:06:42.980 --> 00:06:46.339
You shattered the Heaven’s Tome for the poor and oppressed

00:06:46.939 --> 00:06:48.240
You set your heart for heaven and earth

00:06:48.560 --> 00:06:49.860
and gave purpose to the people

00:06:50.279 --> 00:06:50.920
Now

00:06:51.360 --> 00:06:53.019
you are finally worthy to inherit

00:06:53.279 --> 00:06:54.819
the Three Swords of Evil-Slaying

00:07:20.279 --> 00:07:20.980
So it turns out

00:07:22.279 --> 00:07:25.360
only by fighting for a chance for all beings

00:07:26.060 --> 00:07:29.100
can one master the ultimate move of the Immortal Defying Divine Art

00:07:30.420 --> 00:07:31.980
Three Swords of Evil-Slaying

00:07:33.000 --> 00:07:34.399
First Sword of Evil-Slaying

00:07:34.899 --> 00:07:36.899
Sword of Swallowing Mountains, Severing Mortal Bonds

00:07:44.980 --> 00:07:45.600
Rouge

00:07:46.379 --> 00:07:47.180
Come here, quick

00:07:52.220 --> 00:07:54.000
Husband, I beg you

00:07:54.459 --> 00:07:55.379
Let me go

00:07:56.899 --> 00:07:58.620
I’ve always treated you well

00:07:58.939 --> 00:08:00.660
Now it’s time for you to repay me

00:08:00.959 --> 00:08:04.139
Give me all your power

00:08:08.879 --> 00:08:12.720
Brother Yuanqi, save me

00:08:12.879 --> 00:08:17.259
I was really just used by Dugu Zhantian

00:08:19.720 --> 00:08:21.019
Save me

00:08:21.300 --> 00:08:24.779
I’ll serve you loyally from now on

00:08:31.240 --> 00:08:32.200
Chen Yuanqi

00:08:33.100 --> 00:08:33.960
Do you think

00:08:34.759 --> 00:08:36.779
you still have a chance to defeat me

00:08:37.659 --> 00:08:39.279
Second Sword of Evil-Slaying

00:08:40.720 --> 00:08:42.759
Sword of Annihilating All Laws

00:08:47.879 --> 00:08:48.679
No

00:08:50.559 --> 00:08:52.279
I am the Demon Sect’s Supreme Leader

00:08:52.500 --> 00:08:53.940
I refuse to accept this

00:08:54.919 --> 00:08:56.480
Star-Devouring Demonic Art

00:08:56.679 --> 00:08:58.620
Absorption from Afar

00:09:09.559 --> 00:09:10.720
Third Sword of Evil-Slaying

00:09:11.419 --> 00:09:13.919
I have a sword that sunders heaven and earth